title: 83. Fear & Walking in Your Power
description:
Hey sis!

In this episode, we are talking all about fear, listening to your intuition, and making decisions when it comes to relationships, your career, and life in general- we are getting raw & real and diving into how going back and forth ends up hurting us and our potential in the long run.

Click here to join the waitlist for my 4 month group coaching program, Embodied. Spots are limited- I will only have 10 spots available for this container to keep it as close knit as possible. or visit Beatricekamau.com/groupcoaching
